### Variables
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Ping Check
GET {{host}}/health

### 2. Login
# @name login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "mobileNo": "9888888888",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Select Institution
# Fixed URL to match your app.post route
# @name selection
POST {{host}}/api/auth/select-institution
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "institutionId": "df832fc6-999c-4b73-ac1e-ab5ba4e56cd7"
}

### 4. Get Data (Use the NEW token from the selection response)
GET {{host}}/api/institutions
Authorization: Bearer {{selection.response.body.token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
